                             <title>Life and miracles of Walatta Ṗeṭros</title>
                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.1">
                                    <locus from="5r" to="147rb"/>
                                    <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1509GadlaW">Gadla Walatta
                                        Ṗeṭros</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                        <locus from="5ra" to="5rb"/>
                                        <hi rend="rubric">በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘሃሎ፡ እምቅድመ፡</hi> ዓለም፡ <add place="margin">ወይሄሎ፡ እስከ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡</add> ዘአልቦ፡ ጥንት፡
                                            ወኢተፍጻሜት፡<hi rend="rubric"> እምላክነ፡ በመለኮቱ፡ ወአቡነ፡
                                            በኂሩቱ።</hi> ዘስብሐቲሁ፡ እምኀቤሁ፡ ወውዳሴሁ፡ እምዚአሁ፡ ዘይክል፡ ኵሎ፡ ወአልቦ፡
                                        ዘይስአኖ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨ አጽሕፍ፡ እንከ፡ ንስቲተ፡ አነ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ገብራ፡ <space unit="chars" quantity="7"> </space> እምዜና፡ ስደራ፡ ወእ<hi rend="rubric">ምብዙኅ፡ ገድላቲሃ፡ ወትሩፋቲሃ፡ ለእምነ፡ ቅድስት፡ ወለተ፡
                                            ጴጥ<cb/>ሮስ፡ ሰጻፍ፡ እመ፡ አዕናቊ፡ አዕላፍ ። ። ።</hi>
                                    </incipit>
                                    <note>According to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/9TIZMHAI"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:WendyundKleiner2015WalattaPetros"/><title level="m">The Life and Struggles of Our Mother Walatta Petros: A Seventeenth-Century African Biography of an Ethiopian Woman, Written by Galawdewos</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Wendy Laura</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Belcher</t:surname></author><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Michael</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Kleiner</t:surname></author><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Wendy Laura</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Belcher</t:surname></editor><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Michael</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Kleiner</t:surname></editor><pubPlace>Princeton, NJ–Oxford</pubPlace><publisher>Princeton University Press</publisher><date>2015</date><note type="url">https://books.google.de/books/about/The_Life_and_Struggles_of_Our_Mother_Wal.html?id=ofT8CAAAQBAJ&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;source=kp_read_button&amp;redir_esc=y#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false</note><citedRange unit="page">258, n.258</citedRange></bibl>, <cit><quote>CR omits about two manuscript pages of material that is <supplied reason="subaudible">present</supplied>[...] in all the other manuscripts at our disposal. Since the missing material is a folio´s worth, and resumes halfway through an anecdote midsentence, we assume that either a folio got lost from Abb. 88 or that the scribe of Abb.88 inadvertently skipped one folio while copying.</quote></cit>
                                        Nafisa Valieva, while cataloguing this manuscript, identified that the omitted passages has been supplied on f.1r <ref target="#a1"/>. The ommited portion starts on f. 142v with the word ትቤለኒ, while the scribe resumes with ትቤለ<add place="inline">ኒ</add>,  which suggests a homeoteleuton. The scholars further note, <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/9TIZMHAI"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:WendyundKleiner2015WalattaPetros"/><title level="m">The Life and Struggles of Our Mother Walatta Petros: A Seventeenth-Century African Biography of an Ethiopian Woman, Written by Galawdewos</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Wendy Laura</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Belcher</t:surname></author><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Michael</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Kleiner</t:surname></author><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Wendy Laura</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Belcher</t:surname></editor><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Michael</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Kleiner</t:surname></editor><pubPlace>Princeton, NJ–Oxford</pubPlace><publisher>Princeton University Press</publisher><date>2015</date><note type="url">https://books.google.de/books/about/The_Life_and_Struggles_of_Our_Mother_Wal.html?id=ofT8CAAAQBAJ&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;source=kp_read_button&amp;redir_esc=y#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false</note><citedRange unit="page">271-272</citedRange></bibl>, that the
                                        present manuscript has an <cit>
                                            <quote>alternate ending</quote>
                                        </cit> in comparison to other witnesses.
                                    </note>
                                </msItem>
                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.2.">
                                    <locus from="147va" to="171vb"/>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7073TammeraW">Taʾammǝra Walatta
                                        Ṗeṭros</title>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                        <locus from="147va" to="148rb"/>
                                        <hi rend="rubric">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ </hi>፩አምላክ፡
                                        ዘለዓለም። ዓዲ፡ ናተሉ፡ ጽሒፈ፡ <hi rend="rubric">ተአምረ፡ ዘገብረት፡ እምነ፡
                                            ቡርክት፡ ወለተ፡ ጴጥሮስ። ጸሎታ፡ ወ</hi>በረከተ፡ ረድኤታ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስሌነ፡ ለዓለመ፡
                                        ዓለም፡ አሜን። ስምዑ፡ ንንግርክሙ፡ ኃይለ፡ ተአምር፡ ዘኮነ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ዕረፍታ፡ ለእምነ፡
                                        ብፅዕት፡ <hi rend="rubric">ወለተ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡</hi> ዘሰማዕነ፡ ወዘርኢነ፡
                                        ዘይትገበር፡ በዕለተ፡ ተዝካራ፡ ለለጊዜሁ፡ እም፴ዕለት፡ እስከ፡ ፍጻሜ፡ ዓመት፡ ከመ፡ ወደረ፡
                                        በረከተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ላዕለ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዘኮነ፡ ግብረ፡ ተዝካር፡ ዘይትገበር። ወአሜሃ፡ ተጋብኡ፡
                                        ብዙኃን፡ ሰብእ፡ እምሥራቅ፡ ወእምዕራብ፡ እምአድባር፡ ወእመካናት፡ ወእምገዳማት፡ ወእምኵሉ፡
                                        አኅጉር፡ እለ፡ አልቦሙ፡ ኍልቊ። ቦእምኔሆሙ፡ መምህራን፡ ወቀሳውስት፡ ወዲያቆናት፡ ወመነኮሳት፡
                                        ምስለ፡ ማዕጠንታት፡ ወመስቀላት። ወቦ፡ እምኔሆሙ፡ ነዳያን፡ ወምስኪናን፡ ወዕውራን፡ ወሐንካሳን፡
                                        እስመ፡ ተሰምዓ፡ ዜናሃ፡ ውስተ፡ ኵሉ፡ አጽናፈ፡ ዓለም። ወወሀብዎሙ፡ ብዙኃ፡ መብልዐ፡ ወመስቴ፡
                                        በበማዕርጊሆሙ፡ ወበበመጠሆሙ፡ እስከ፡ ጸግቡ፡ ወአትረፉ። ፩ተአምር፡ ዘኮነ፡ ሶቤሃ። ወይቤሉ፡
                                        ሀለወ፡ ኅዳጥ፡ ኅቡአ፡ መጠነ፡ ፩ኅብስት፡ በዓቢይ፡ ጋን፡ ዘተረፈ፡ እምነ፡ ተዝካር። ወእምዝ፡
                                        ተረክበ፡ እንዘ፡ ይፈልሕ፡ ወይመልዕ፡ እስከ፡ ላዕሉ፡ ወይትከዓው። </incipit>
                                </msItem>
                                <note>According to <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/9TIZMHAI"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:WendyundKleiner2015WalattaPetros"/><title level="m">The Life and Struggles of Our Mother Walatta Petros: A Seventeenth-Century African Biography of an Ethiopian Woman, Written by Galawdewos</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Wendy Laura</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Belcher</t:surname></author><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Michael</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Kleiner</t:surname></author><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Wendy Laura</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Belcher</t:surname></editor><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Michael</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Kleiner</t:surname></editor><pubPlace>Princeton, NJ–Oxford</pubPlace><publisher>Princeton University Press</publisher><date>2015</date><note type="url">https://books.google.de/books/about/The_Life_and_Struggles_of_Our_Mother_Wal.html?id=ofT8CAAAQBAJ&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;source=kp_read_button&amp;redir_esc=y#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false</note><citedRange>330-334</citedRange></bibl>, the supplication and the colophon below are attested only in the present manuscript.</note>
                                <explicit xml:lang="gez" type="supplication">
                                    <locus from="171ra" to="172ra"/> ዘአጽሐፍነ፡ እለ፡ መጻእነ፡ ወእለ፡ ተጋባእነ፡
                                    በዛቲ፡ ዕለት፡ ለሰሚዓ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ገድላቲሃ፡ ወተአምራቲሃ፡ ለእምነ፡ ቡርክት፡ ወለተ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ </explicit>
                                <colophon xml:id="coloph1" xml:lang="gez">
                                    <locus target="#172r"/> ዘተጽሕፈ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ገድል፡ በ፸፻ወ፪፻ እም፯ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡
                                    በዘመነ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ አመ፡ ፳ወረቡዑ፡ አባቅቴ፡ በ፲ወ፯ መጥቅዕ። <del rend="erasure"/>ወተፈጸመ፡ በወርኃ፡ የካቲት፡ በዕለተ፡ ረቡዕ፡ በ፱ ሰዓት፡ ለዘሰረቆ፡
                                    ወለዘተዓገሎ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ በሥልጣኖሙ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን። ወበቃሎሙ፡ ዘ፫፻ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን።
