                                <item xml:id="a6">
                                    <locus target="#5ra"/>
                                    <desc type="Supplication"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ተማሕፀንኩ፡ በእምነ፡ ወለተ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ኃጥዕ፡ ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡
                                        ነፍስየ፡ እምነፍስኪ፡ ኢትሌልያ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡ ለይኩን፡ ለይኩን። የተጻፈበት፡
                                        ወቄት፡ ታ፭፡ ጨው፡</q>
                                    <q xml:lang="eng">I, the sinner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13644WaldaGiyorgis">Walda Giyorgis</persName>, entrust
                                        myself to our mother <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9848Walatta">Walatta Ṗeṭros</persName>, 'Do
                                        not separate my soul from yours in eternity, amen!' May it
                                        be thus, may it be thus!</q>
                                </item>
